Subject: [slayzone] slayzone: Phase 11.2 settings SettingsHost + Labs tab
 wiring
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

First real data wire for the settings surface.

Adds slayzone.settings.mojom.SettingsHost — a scalar string KV
interface with GetString(key) => (value) and SetString(key, value) =>
(ok). Every Phase 11 tab with scalar settings reads / writes through
this single host.

Browser side: slayzone_settings_host.{cc,h} forwards to sidecar
settings:get / settings:set. SlayzoneSettingsUI now owns a
SlayzoneSettingsHost (std::unique_ptr) and implements BindInterface.
binders_desktop registers ForWebUI<SlayzoneSettingsUI>.Add<
settings::mojom::SettingsHost>.

Scope fences held — no SlayzoneBrowserView edits. Labs is the first
tab consuming the host; outer-repo commit ships the sidecar handler +
React port.
